    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>I'm not going to lie  - sending out nearly a million emails announcing that you've had a <a href="https://drupal.org/news/130529SecurityUpdate">security breach</a> is no fun. Honestly, it's one of the worst things I have ever had to do in my professional life. It's true that <a href="http://www.voanews.com/content/cyber-criminals-/1670236.html">cyber-crime is growing fast</a>, and we are not the only organization to face this dilemma, but this isn't the kind of club membership you want to keep.</p>
